@startuml
title AI智能分析与处方推荐功能时序图

actor "医生" as Doctor
participant "ChatController\nchatPlain()" as ChatController
participant "ConsultationService\ngetMessages()" as ConsultationService
participant "KnowledgeGraphService\nanalyzeWithKnowledgeGraph()" as KGService
participant "ChatClient\nprompt().call()" as ChatClient
participant "ConsultationService\nappendMessage()" as MessageService
participant "Neo4j图数据库" as Neo4j

Doctor -> ChatController: 输入患者症状描述\nGET /ai/chat/plain
activate ChatController

ChatController -> ConsultationService: 获取问诊历史记录\ngetMessages(consultationId)
activate ConsultationService
ConsultationService --> ChatController: 返回历史对话消息
deactivate ConsultationService

ChatController -> KGService: 执行知识图谱分析\nanalyzeWithKnowledgeGraph(症状文本)
activate KGService

KGService -> KGService: 提取症状实体\nfindSymptomNamesInRawText()
KGService -> Neo4j: 查询匹配的症状节点
activate Neo4j
Neo4j --> KGService: 返回症状实体列表
deactivate Neo4j

KGService -> KGService: 匹配相关证型\nfindSyndromesBySymptomNames()
KGService -> Neo4j: 查询证型关系网络
activate Neo4j
Neo4j --> KGService: 返回证型及权重
deactivate Neo4j

KGService -> KGService: 获取详细信息\nfindTypicalSymptomsBySyndromeId()\nfindFormulasBySyndromeId()
KGService -> Neo4j: 查询典型症状和方剂
activate Neo4j
Neo4j --> KGService: 返回完整知识数据
deactivate Neo4j

KGService --> ChatController: 返回知识图谱分析结果\n包含症状、证型、方剂信息
deactivate KGService

ChatController -> ChatController: 构建增强提示词\n整合历史对话和知识图谱结果

ChatController -> ChatClient: 调用大语言模型生成回答\nprompt(增强提示词).call()
activate ChatClient
ChatClient --> ChatController: 返回AI生成的辨证分析和处方建议
deactivate ChatClient

ChatController -> MessageService: 保存AI回答到数据库\nappendMessage(consultationId, "AI", "assistant", 回答)
activate MessageService
MessageService --> ChatController: 确认消息保存成功
deactivate MessageService

ChatController -> ChatController: 清理回复格式\ncleanResponse()

ChatController --> Doctor: 返回智能分析和处方推荐\n包含辨证思路和用药建议
deactivate ChatController

@enduml


@startuml
title 病历编辑与打印导出功能时序图

actor "医生" as Doctor
participant "ConsultationReportController\nreportHtml()" as ReportController
participant "ConsultationReportService\nbuild()" as ReportService
participant "ConsultationService\nfindById()" as ConsultationService
participant "DoctorMapper\nfindById()" as DoctorMapper
participant "PatientMapper\nfindById()" as PatientMapper
participant "ConsultationReportService\nbuildPdf()" as PdfService
participant "PdfRendererBuilder" as PdfRenderer
participant "浏览器" as Browser

Doctor -> ReportController: 请求病历预览页面\nGET /api/consultations/{id}/report/html
activate ReportController

ReportController -> ReportService: 构建病历数据\nbuild(consultationId)
activate ReportService

ReportService -> ConsultationService: 获取问诊基本信息\nfindById(consultationId)
activate ConsultationService
ConsultationService --> ReportService: 返回问诊记录
deactivate ConsultationService

ReportService -> DoctorMapper: 获取医生信息\nfindById(doctorId)
activate DoctorMapper
DoctorMapper --> ReportService: 返回医生资料
deactivate DoctorMapper

ReportService -> PatientMapper: 获取患者信息\nfindById(patientId)
activate PatientMapper
PatientMapper --> ReportService: 返回患者信息
deactivate PatientMapper

ReportService -> ReportService: 解析AI建议内容\nsplitAiMessage()\nparseHerbs()

ReportService --> ReportController: 返回完整病历数据对象\nConsultationReportVO
deactivate ReportController

ReportController -> ReportController: 生成可编辑的HTML页面\n包含四个可修改区域

ReportController --> Doctor: 返回病历预览页面\n支持在线编辑症状、证型、药方、医嘱
deactivate ReportController

Doctor -> Browser: 在浏览器中编辑病历内容\n修改症状描述、调整证型、完善药方、补充医嘱
activate Browser
Browser --> Doctor: 实时预览编辑效果
deactivate Browser

Doctor -> ReportController: 提交编辑后的病历\nPOST /api/consultations/{id}/report/pdf
activate ReportController

ReportController -> PdfService: 生成PDF文档\nbuildPdf(consultationId, editedDraft)
activate PdfService

PdfService -> PdfService: 构建打印用HTML内容\nbuildPrintableHtml()

PdfService -> PdfRenderer: 创建PDF渲染器\nPdfRendererBuilder()
activate PdfRenderer
PdfRenderer -> PdfRenderer: 设置中文字体\ntryUseWindowsFont()
PdfRenderer -> PdfRenderer: 转换HTML为PDF
PdfRenderer --> PdfService: 生成PDF字节流
deactivate PdfRenderer

PdfService --> ReportController: 返回PDF文件字节数组
deactivate PdfService

ReportController --> Doctor: 返回可下载的PDF病历文件\n包含医生编辑后的所有内容
deactivate ReportController

@enduml